  "description": "<i>Infestation</i> is an arcade 2 kb maze game, created for 2011 Minigame Competition. As an elite space marine the player is teleported to training spaceship &quot;Virgo&quot; taken over by alien beings. The ship is a maze of rooms and corridors. Each chamber is inhabited by two aliens, reflecting constantly and regularly from the walls. Rescuing all six rookie female cadets requires avoiding aliens, finding proper door switches and reaching the girls. The player may use a plasma gun to temporarily freeze the enemy. Contact with hostile creature means a certain death.",
